{"tid":590571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入]終於明點解特惠牌啲嘢會咁平","createTime":"2018-03-12T17:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T09:17:13.000Z","uid":55552,"like":3,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c42586343320c85360463999e23ef5863a382bf1","tid":590571,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"話說今日路過百佳，醒起屋企啲鬚刨刀片就快用晒，於是就入去睇下<br />\n<br />\n結果一望就當堂嚇一跳，屌你我支鋒速3一舊水都唔使，你嗰幾塊刀片就賣兩舊水，吉列你究竟係賣鬚刨定賣刀片<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/012135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F012135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=94cc50c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正係我計較之際，眼尾睄到特惠牌鬚刨，當時我簡直唔夠膽相信自己嘅眼睛，只係賣15.9，平過吉列10倍有突，真係無改錯名，好撚特惠呀屌<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/012142_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F012142_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b0773b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然，我感覺到一絲異樣，似乎舊特惠牌刀片上面黐住咗啲污糟嘢，於是我將佢拎起，仔細一望<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/012357_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F012357_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=61c28cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我當時個表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話，有時真係唔好貪小便宜，如果唔係，你都唔知會有咩驚喜等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131bac54bda0eea0532d4cdad87e27bc6ca02a68","tid":590571,"uid":174110,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:12:27.000Z","msg":"拎過另一盒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708932cbefdf87aab39506b315af94ff7aa8b39c","tid":590571,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"乜撚野"},{"pid":"2956856cb29f98a4ff56a77159b9b0e3623f1025","tid":590571,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:23:12.000Z","msg":"做咩柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de8b2e2edcce77f1cb37c78e89a6bc525c2a7e9","tid":590571,"uid":85416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎過另一盒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係"},{"pid":"63e7a44770761a690483202e38560c65ebb184c8","tid":590571,"uid":27416,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:28:00.000Z","msg":"有鬚都十幾歲啦<br />\n仲係咁撚on9都有"},{"pid":"2fcecf3b0793b1cde82d78b1a81ee87dc8d32baa","tid":590571,"uid":99863,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:29:55.000Z","msg":"你唔係以為係因為多咗隻野，所以先會咁平啊哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41566534f11e24ffcac6aaf7899fce780e94b18","tid":590571,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63e7a44770761a690483202e38560c65ebb184c8","tid":590571,"uid":27416,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:28:00.000Z","msg":"有鬚都十幾歲啦<br />\n仲係咁撚on9都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:30:37.000Z","msg":"成個弱智咁<br />\n好似茶餐廳見到隻蚊仔又fb又食環又乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463ace1ad462dff64d974b25919c5f508dc65751","tid":590571,"uid":34793,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:32:05.000Z","msg":"屌 生鬚嫁啦 大個仔啦 咪咁on9得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fa726959392cd3095a91cd3bbb20585c096d8c","tid":590571,"uid":136221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"你係咪覺得會過千正評先po出黎以為自己好醒"},{"pid":"f830cc03f75ebb2015d7a21c977e65c7cddac900","tid":590571,"uid":148224,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:55:53.000Z","msg":"樓主路過百佳但行入惠康買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2fcfe0fc05a9c515ee19c2e38a117968400302","tid":590571,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f830cc03f75ebb2015d7a21c977e65c7cddac900","tid":590571,"uid":148224,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:55:53.000Z","msg":"樓主路過百佳但行入惠康買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T19:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be791105f28ceed0f9b08354882b4b48d50f996f","tid":590571,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc2fcfe0fc05a9c515ee19c2e38a117968400302","tid":590571,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f830cc03f75ebb2015d7a21c977e65c7cddac900","tid":590571,"uid":148224,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:55:53.000Z","msg":"樓主路過百佳但行入惠康買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T19:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T20:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h